0px) 100vw, 900px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/7c2a9910650c92de832acebf2884044a/1cfc2/Advantagesofdevops.png\"\n            alt=\"devops\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">devops</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>You are a cool devops engineer, confident in the basic set of applications and do not even think about learning programming languages? It is in vain because the devetests are increasingly responsible for more complex infrastructure tools. For example, Golang in Kubernetes will allow you to easily and simply launch new services, and delivering code to production will no longer be a star-studded task. If you search for a job, you will definitely stand out from other competitors!</p>\n<p>Our DeVos explained why it is important to learn programming languages in 2025:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Understanding the development process: Programming language knowledge helps DevOps engineers better understand how developers work, which contributes to more effective team-to-team interaction.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Working with cloud technologies: In 2025, cloud solutions will continue to gain popularity. Programming languages are needed to work with cloud services API, server logic and resource management.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Security: Programming language knowledge allows for a better understanding of vulnerabilities and application protection methods, which is critical to ensuring the security of DevOps processes.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Adaptation to new technologies: The technological landscape is constantly changing. The ability to program allows you to assimilate new tools and technologies faster, which makes specialists more competitive.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Need Additional Help?</p>\n<p>If your team requires further assistance with DevOps monitoring or a range of solutions that help organizations accelerate software development and delivery through automation, collaboration, and continuous improvement, weâ€™re here to help!  Visit our website to explore the full range of services we offer. You can also submit a request for a free consultation, and our experts will be ready to assist you in optimizing your DevOps processes. Let us partner with you to enhance your development workflow and deliver outstanding results!</p>\n<p><strong>We wish you a great mood and interesting tasks!</strong></p>","wordCount":{"words":296}},"author":{"frontmatter":{"authorAlias":"Zakruzhnaya","author":"Olga Zakruzhnaya","authorPosition":"Marketing specialist","authorPhoto":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/d4a57/author.jpg","srcSet":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/40657/author.jpg 16w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/77b35/author.jpg 32w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/d4a57/author.jpg 64w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/19e71/author.jpg 128w","sizes":"(min-width: 64px) 64px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/e8e20/author.avif 16w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/b6d61/author.avif 32w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/2e71d/author.avif 64w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/3c49f/author.avif 128w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 64px) 64px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/e789a/author.webp 16w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/ef6ff/author.webp 32w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/8257c/author.webp 64w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/6766a/author.webp 128w","typ